README
--------------

Install stramer in Raspberrypi

 sudo apt-get install motion

Edit configuration file to turn off local streaming

 change file /etc/motion/motion.conf

Run Demon

 sudo /etc/init.d/motion restart


Install flask send the commands from webpage to Raspberry Pi  .

pip install Flask
from flask import Flask
from flask import Flask, render_template, request

Download package and store the robot.html in the templates folder which is in the same location of python code.


Run python script in Raspberry pi which will provide the webpage in specific IP and port.

From the PC we can access the webpage with IP address of RaspberryPi and can control with arrows in the webpage
